## Critical Import Rules

ALWAYS import from domain barrels, NEVER from internal paths:

```typescript
// CORRECT
import { Component } from '@/domains/{domain}'

// FORBIDDEN - This will fail ESLint
import { Component } from '@/domains/{domain}/components/{feature}/component'
```

## Tenant Isolation (Security Critical)

EVERY database query MUST include tenant_id:

```typescript
// CORRECT
prisma.table.findMany({ where: { tenant_id: tenantId, ...filters } })

// WRONG - Security vulnerability!
prisma.table.findMany({ where: { ...filters } })
```

